{"tid":1543612,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【9月8日　百萬人齊集美國領事館】 當日真係大撚鑊！大家遺漏左至關重要嘅一點！求幫推！","createTime":"2019-09-05T08:55:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T05:27:16.000Z","uid":14328,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"431ac9c5ec9c54f2a54424470e734345c08b3c8b","tid":1543612,"uid":14328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:55:46.000Z","msg":"文宣組手足<br />\n<br />\n通過＜＜香港人權與民主法案＞＞<br />\n支持美國追討中國萬億美元債<br />\n故然重要<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但係大家漏左一樣好重要既野：關心美國風災！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3244050/org/200bd661f5df1879d5d155ef73f62d7d.JPG/4CP3dGCqqXtd76zsGE41620xAAC3IjBemjy555o8uec?v=w960r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3244050%2Forg%2F200bd661f5df1879d5d155ef73f62d7d.JPG%2F4CP3dGCqqXtd76zsGE41620xAAC3IjBemjy555o8uec%3Fv%3Dw960r16_9&h=196eb2b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國風災至今已經死左２０人，損傷難以估計。<br />\n<br />\n當代香港人已經進化成香港人2.0<br />\n唔再係以前唯利是圖、貪生怕死、物質唯上既香港人<br />\n而係勇不畏死、堅守信念、支持民主既高等人種。<br />\n<br />\n作為優秀民族，見到文明國家有難，出手幫拖乃係義不容辭。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">買完物質銀包仲有剩既，不妨捐埋錢比美國協助災後重建</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a68cab19c5efd37b045b24f475d3e74a307cf7e5","tid":1543612,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:56:00.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s=